WITH element_counts AS (
    SELECT element1, element2, COUNT(bond_id) AS bond_count
    FROM (
        SELECT atom.element AS element1, atom2.element AS element2, bond.bond_id
        FROM atom
        INNER JOIN connected ON atom.atom_id = connected.atom_id
        INNER JOIN atom AS atom2 ON connected.atom_id2 = atom2.atom_id
        INNER JOIN bond ON connected.bond_id = bond.bond_id
    ) AS combined_elements
    GROUP BY element1, element2
),
most_common_combination AS (
    SELECT element1, element2
    FROM element_counts
    ORDER BY bond_count DESC
    LIMIT 1
),
total_bonds AS (
    SELECT COUNT(bond_id) AS total_bond_count
    FROM bond
),
bonds_with_most_common_combination AS (
    SELECT COUNT(*) AS common_bond_count
    FROM (
        SELECT atom.element AS element1, atom2.element AS element2, bond.bond_id
        FROM atom
        INNER JOIN connected ON atom.atom_id = connected.atom_id
        INNER JOIN atom AS atom2 ON connected.atom_id2 = atom2.atom_id
        INNER JOIN bond ON connected.bond_id = bond.bond_id
    ) AS combined_elements
    WHERE (element1, element2) IN (SELECT element1, element2 FROM most_common_combination)
)
SELECT (common_bond_count * 100.0 / total_bond_count) AS percentage
FROM bonds_with_most_common_combination, total_bonds;
